      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Top, tail and slice the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into thin discs</p><p>Top, tail and slice the <strong>parsnip<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into thin discs</p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Crush the <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and discard the skins</p>",
