    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skin on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> and <strong>beetroot liquid</strong> to a pot with a matching lid with 750ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until fork-tender</p>",
