    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, roll the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Combine the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong> lemon </strong>with<strong> </strong>the<strong> crème fraîche </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>lemon</strong> <strong>crème fraîche</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 4,
