    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pine nuts are golden, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and transfer the <strong>honey</strong> <strong>roasted beetroot & onion </strong>to the pot with the potatoes</p><p>Add the <strong>roasted garlic</strong>, <strong>parsnip</strong>,<strong> carrot </strong>and the juice of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat – this is your <strong>soup</strong></p>",
