      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> borscht-inspired roast beetroot soup </strong>in bowls</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>lemon</strong> <strong>crème fraîche </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>chopped dill </strong>and <strong>toasted pine nuts</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> toasted ciabatta </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
